once upon a time the was Crocodile 
who went out to get food for his wife
while exploring large river he found 
a Monkey sleeping on a large fruit tree
he asked the Monkey that he could get
some fruit for his family, the Monkey
replied "yes, friend" he takes the fruit
to his wife,then she askes "where did you
get em'?" he replie's "i got it from a Monkey." 
